lurred-lines\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/74658000/jpg/_74658793_74658576.jpg\" alt=\"Image of Kirsty Walk\" />Blurred Lines:The New Battle of the Sexes</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t<p>BBC Two:Kirsty Wark investigates </p>\r\n\t\t<hr />\r\n\t</li>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t<li class=\"medium-image \">\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" programme-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1399025627429\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/articles/4RNfz3DCczPPlCwy8wgjxpt/young-choristers-of-the-year-2014\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/74601000/jpg/_74601507_ycoy.jpg\" alt=\"Young Choristers and presenter\" />Young Choristers of the Year 2014</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t<p>Radio 2 search for the UK&#039;s top choristers </p>\r\n\t\t<hr />\r\n\t</li>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t<li class=\"medium-image \">\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" programme-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1383321623227\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p002vsn4\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/70855000/jpg/_70855606_hands.jpg\" alt=\"Hands\" />Heart and Soul</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t<p>Personal approaches to belief and spirituality from around the world</p>\r\n\t\t<hr />\r\n\t</li>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t<li class=\"medium-image \">\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" programme-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1353925573306\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b006qnbd\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/70804000/jpg/_70804980_estourtonbbc.jpg\" alt=\"Edward Stourton\" />Sunday on Radio Four<span class=\"gvl3-icon-wrapper\"><span class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-invert-listen\"> Listen</span></span></a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\